PEACH UP (WIP WAP):     LIVES=$D28C
PEACH UP (HAMMERTJE)    $CE03,$CE02
PEACH UP (PEACH SLOT):  GOLD=$6070
PEACH UP (HYPERBLOCK):  BALLS=$5D16
PEACH UP (SHOOTER):     BOMBS&LIVES=$D209,$D208
HYDEFOS:                ENERGIE&LIVES&SCORE=$C11C,$D404,$D406
NINJA DEXTER:           MAGIC=$D46F
PACMANIA:               LIVES=$D033
YS 1:                   GOLD&EXP&HP=$CFC7,$CFC9,$CFC3
YS 2:                   GOLD&EXP&MP=$0196,$0102,$0104
YS 3:                   HP&EXP&RING=$7FA7,$7FA0,$7EA0
PRINCESS:               LIVES=$CE06
FAMICLE PARODIC:        LIVES=$E003
FAMICLE PARODIC II:     LIVES=$C008
LAST TESTAMENT:         GRENADES=$59DE
USAS:                   COINS=$C259
MARAYA:                 GOLD&FIRE,LIVES,LIFE,KEYS,BOMBS=$CCD4,$CD74,$CCBC,$CCD3,$CD75,$CD76
TWINKLE STAR GAMES:     LIVES=$4052
NO FUSS:                LIVES=$7FFE
GREATEST DRIVER:        QUALIFY LAPS (P1)=$A256
GREATEST DRIVER:        QUALIFY LAPS (P2)=$A28B
ALESTE SPECIAL:         LIVES=$D080  LEVEL=$D00B
